              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Encapsulated solutions containing approximately 1",
                "micro gram of 241-Pu were irradiated pneumatically at",
                "a neutron flux of 1.0x10**13 n/cm2/sec."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The resultant precipitate of silver antiomonide,",
                "dissolved in dil. HNO3, was counted on a 45 cc HPGe",
                "detector coupled to a 4 K MCA in live time. The",
                "resolution of the detector was 2.2 keV at 1332 keV.",
                "The gamma spectra indicated that there was no",
                "contamination from other fission products in the",
                "separated antimony isotopes."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "RCHEM",
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " After the irradiation antimony was",
                "separated from the irradiated target solution by",
                "distilling antimony hydride and collecting into",
                "silver nitrate solution. The resultant precipitate of",
                "silver antiomonide, dissolved in dil. HNO3, was counted",
                "on a 45 cc HPGe  detector coupled to a 4 K MCA in live",
                "time."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "AREA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " From the photopeak areas of the gamma rays of",
                "the nuclides' independent isomeric yields were",
                "determined using usual decay-growth equations after",
                "correcting for the precursor contribution."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The error on an individual measurement is",
                "about 15 % which is the compounded error due to",
                "counting statistics, the uncertainties on the",
                "gamma-ray abundances, the fractional cumulative yield",
                " (fCY)128-Sn, the irradiation and separation",
                "times and the half lives. The errors quoted on the",
                "mean isomeric yield ratios are the precision of the",
                "measurements."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "MISC-COL": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MISC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " fission fragment angular momenta Jrms"
              ]
            }
          ],
